snippet.title: MicroHorrorArcade Trilogy I - Andy's Story | RELEASE DATE TRAILER
snippet.description:
This bundle of games I've been working on for the last month or so is available NOW on Patreon for $1 and Thursday on Itchio for $1.50! It's my half of a collab project with Dave Microwaves Games! Details in the video below:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=seblsJuad5s

Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/MicroHorrorArcade
